{"tid":437128,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬雲斥千億設達摩院！大搞NASA計劃","createTime":"2017-10-15T16:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T00:43:51.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8eca0018c992b9a2136e3f04fe36f22c875c2508","tid":437128,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"近日由阿里巴巴舉辦的2017杭州&bull;雲棲大會開幕，阿里巴巴集團首席技術官張建鋒表示，將成立「達摩院」，計畫三年內對新技術投資超過1000億元人民幣，將與各大高校合作成立實驗室。首批公佈的研究領域包括：量子計算、機器學習、視覺計算、自然語言處理、人機自然交互、晶片技術、感測器技術、嵌入式系統等，涵蓋機器智能、智聯網、金融科技等多個產業領域。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171011/large/1507699477_6794.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171011%2Flarge%2F1507699477_6794.jpg&h=18155c1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n另外，阿里雲與中科院宣佈合作發佈量子計算雲平台。在2015年7月，阿里雲已聯合中科院成立量子計算實驗室，共同開發量子電腦。中國科學院院士潘建偉表示，希望到明年，能實現50個量子比特的操作；未來十年能實現數百個量子比特的操作，在特定領域的計算能力達到目前全世界計算能力的100萬倍。量子電腦是指利用量子相干疊加原理，理論上具有超快的平行計算和模擬能力的電腦，較現有電腦的計算能力可無限倍提升。量子計算是阿里巴巴「NASA計劃」的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n馬雲表示，希望阿里巴巴集團未來的利潤是由技術產生，而不是市場規模所帶來。1,000億元人民幣是啟動資金，後期達摩院要實現自營自理，活得比阿里要久。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20171011/57317797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20171011%2F57317797&d=Qn7MYfq1I5E%2F%2Fjqkniha%2BAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=fee5646e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20171011%2F57317797&h=6376f8c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20171011/57317797</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20171011/57317912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20171011%2F57317912&d=Qn7MYfq1I5E%2F%2Fjqkniha%2BAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=edb78788\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20171011%2F57317912&h=5ed2224a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20171011/57317912</a>"},{"pid":"d19c513c173bae574ad74fefaf9f2ab281039951","tid":437128,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"達摩院一詞來自少林武術，意即研究本派武術的學院，後被借用作形容企業的核心技術研究機構。「達摩院」首批公布的學術諮詢委員會10人中，有3名中國兩院院士、5名美國科學院院士，包括世界人工智能泰斗Michael I. Jordan、分佈式計算（Distributed computing）大家李凱、人類基因組計劃負責人George M. Church等。作為最高學術諮詢機構，該委員會對研究方向、重點發展領域、重大任務和目標等學術問題提供諮詢建議。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170514/420_3e4e1736f94c272ac467a2cccac550db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170514%2F420_3e4e1736f94c272ac467a2cccac550db.jpg&h=382fab9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">&uarr; 馬雲從小愛讀武俠小說、長年打太極，阿里巴巴幾乎每間辦公室都個有出自金庸小說的「武林別稱」，例如馬雲的辦公室是「桃花島」，他本人暱稱則是「風清揚」。</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n另外，在「達摩院」計劃公布前，還有13名頂級科學家前往阿里總部座談，包括中國唯一的圖靈獎得主姚期智院士、中國量子力學第一人潘建偉院士等。<br />\n<br />\nNASA是美國太空總署的英文簡稱。今年3月，馬雲在公司首屆技術大會上啓動「NASA計劃」，稱要在未來20年組建強大的獨立研發部門，建立新的機制，並建構世界第五大經濟體，為服務20億人儲備核心科技。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171012/s00013/1507745378812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171012%2Fs00013%2F1507745378812&d=Qn7MYfq1I5E%2F%2Fjqkniha%2BAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=564fb5fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171012%2Fs00013%2F1507745378812&h=1cfbe8ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171012/s00013/1507745378812</a>"},{"pid":"034d9f4836c7f75f033343eea7340fd21c1b487f","tid":437128,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"一千億黑錢"},{"pid":"d59adbd1d4b1eda2435aeb86f8dc16c6c579ee9a","tid":437128,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:06:14.000Z","msg":"唔好又步樂視後塵好了"},{"pid":"2427ac79fc50b2fa35caf9abd6c97bd9534a6e2c","tid":437128,"uid":5166,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/010701_b8c1dd8e8d38088d28149e801e44ecc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F010701_b8c1dd8e8d38088d28149e801e44ecc8.jpg&h=cfcc7971&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f41d4e78f79a0a6dfb476981e87f151828d7c27","tid":437128,"uid":36421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/010701_b8c1dd8e8d38088d28149e801e44ecc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F010701_b8c1dd8e8d38088d28149e801e44ecc8.jpg&h=cfcc7971&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己係老細咪唔洗要人工<br />\n未碰過錢買嘢叫跟班去買咪得<br />\n對錢無興趣但可以對賺錢同名利有興趣<br />\n個人夠離地而家搞nasa岩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425cac1b688b2ca4339c9fc40036785bbeb44d63","tid":437128,"uid":11171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:23:30.000Z","msg":"有錢到傻撚左 佢想點咪點囉 咪又係扮哂野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898c8c45c8f0fd966570dd04dee5c439c45617b1","tid":437128,"uid":39329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:39:17.000Z","msg":"靠果網賣老番野發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5957ff951b59d1f214ad672c9b39afc4bfaef6","tid":437128,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07fefb3d8e38ade2e32525